  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 425\u00b0F (220\u00b0C). Rinse oysters under running water.",
    "Mix worcestershire sauce, smoked paprika, lime juice, minced garlic, olive oil, salt, and pepper in a bowl.",
    "Place oysters on a baking sheet lined with parchment paper. Pour the spice mixture over each oyster.",
    "Bake for 10 minutes or until oysters are cooked through and crispy.",
    "Serve immediately."
